  ('judicial-d3df8a4a-moex-00143', 'judicial-d3df8a4a', 'judicial-d3df8a4a-moex-111-9bdab6d6', 'sub-judicial-d3df8a4a-04', NULL, 'essay', '丁一公司進、銷資料明細如下表：
