  ('judicial-d3df8a4a-moex-00144', 'judicial-d3df8a4a', 'judicial-d3df8a4a-moex-111-9bdab6d6', 'sub-judicial-d3df8a4a-04', NULL, 'essay', '所得稅法所指之納稅義務人為何？獨資、合夥組織之營利事業是否為營
